  "title": "Retail Sales Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Retail Associate</strong></p>\n<p>Home &amp; Décor Superstore (Wholly owned by King Koil Singapore)</p>\n<p>Please join our team if you are a service orientated and hardworking sales associate with furniture retail experience.  We also welcome those who are keen but without related experience or fresh from schools. Every of our King Koil Ashley Furniture Homestore carry a full range of furniture and a complete King Koil Mattress Gallery.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Serves customers by helping them select products</li>\n  <li>Drive sales through engagement of customers, suggestive selling and sharing product knowledge.</li>\n  <li>Responds to customers’ questions ·</li>\n  <li>Able to share store promotion mechanics and merchandise with customers</li>\n  <li>Maintain and upkeep of showroom display items in proper order, assist with receiving and stocking merchandise.</li>\n  <li>Able to use the computerized Point of Sales system to close orders.</li>\n  <li>Training will be provided in both products and operations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements &amp; Skills:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Fresh graduate/ Minimum Higher Secondary education or ITE and a fast leaner can apply.</li>\n  <li>Those with related furniture retail sales experience will be an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Bilingual in English &amp; Mandarin, good listening and possess good people skills</li>\n  <li>A good team player with positive attitude</li>\n  <li>Must be result oriented and able to work independently</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Remuneration – Basic salary package with commission.</li>\n  <li>Full time job- 6 working days a week with 6 off days per month, required to work on Public holidays and weekend.</li>\n  <li>Working hour: 11am to 8pm.</li>\n  <li>On job Training and uniform will be provided</li>\n  <li>Medical benefits / insurance</li>\n</ul>",
